# docs/dist/ holds the source READMEs that `make package-vscode` /
# `make publish-vscode` swap into place as README.md for the vsce
# invocation. Exclude the whole dir so the swap-source files don't
# appear alongside the swapped-in README.md inside the VSIX.
# (The icon under docs/assets/ is still shipped — it's referenced by
# package.json#icon.)
docs/dist/
